// Minimal Win32 resource script for WKOpenVR.exe. Embeds an application
// icon so the Start menu shortcut, taskbar, alt-tab, and File Explorer all
// render an icon instead of the generic blank application graphic. The icon
// itself is the SC standalone icon as a placeholder until the umbrella
// gets its own brand mark; both products share the calibration core so this
// is not a regression in identity.
//
// Resource ID 1 is the convention Windows looks for when picking a shell
// icon from an exe (it loads the lowest-numbered ICON resource).

1 ICON "openvr-pair.ico"
